OL,3,CBeijing half marathon results annulled
OL,4,Cafter cheating claims
OL,6,Fauthorities have annulled the results
OL,7,Fof this year's Beijing half marathon,
OL,8,Ffollowing accusations that a trio of
OL,9,Frunners deliberately threw the race.
OL,11,FChinese long-distance runner He Jie
OL,12,Fwas after finishing a second ahead of
OL,13,Fthree African athletes - Robert Keter,
OL,14,FWilly Mnangat and Dejene Hailu.
OL,16,FBut video footage of the half
OL,17,Fmarathon's ending sparked claims of
OL,18,Fcheating, when it appeared that He was
OL,19,Fushered to move into first place
OL,20,Fwithout any challenge from the lead
OL,21,Fracers.
