OL,3,CBeijing half marathon results annulled
OL,4,Cafter cheating claims
OL,6,FThe Beijing Half Marathon Organising
OL,7,FCommittee has now retrospectively
OL,8,Fdisqualified He and the trio of
OL,9,FAfrican runners.
OL,11,F"The match results of He Jie, Willy
OL,12,FMnangat, Dejene Bikila and Robert
OL,13,FKeter will be cancelled, the trophies,
OL,14,Fmedals and bonuses will be recovered
OL,15,Fand this case will be reported to the
OL,16,FChinese Athletics Association for
OL,17,Frecord," a statement read.
