OL,3,CBeijing half marathon results annulled
OL,4,Cafter cheating claims
OL,6,F"Issue a notice of criticism to the
OL,7,FBeijing Sports Competition Management
OL,8,Fand International Exchange Center and
OL,9,Fwill severely deal with relevant
OL,10,Fpersonnel."
OL,12,FHe - who is considered one of China's
OL,13,Fmost promising long-distance runners -
OL,14,Fappeared to look unimpressed after
OL,15,Fwinning the event.
OL,17,FIn contrast, Mnangat, Bikila and Keter
OL,18,Fcould be seen smiling and applauding
OL,19,FHe's race win.
