OL,3,CBeijing half marathon results annulled
OL,4,Cafter cheating claims
OL,6,FRace organisers said they would launch
OL,7,Fan investigation shortly after the
OL,8,Fhalf marathon had concluded.
OL,10,FThe Beijing Half Marathon Organising
OL,11,FCommittee added that it felt "deeply
OL,12,Fguilty and sincerely apologise to all
OL,13,Fwalks of life" for not recognising the
OL,14,Ffoul play sooner.
