OL,6,F"We learn the lessons deeply in the
OL,7,Ffuture work, draw references from one
OL,8,Fexample, continuously improve our
OL,9,Fwork, further promote the spirit of
OL,10,Fsports, as well as improve the level
OL,11,Fand quality of competitions," a
OL,12,Fstatement read.
